us stehen zentrale Techniken wie Bezeugen, Wahrsprechen, Übersetzen und Fürsprechen sowie Medien wie Formulare, Protokolle und Datenbanken.  afunded by Backlisttransformation EOSC Future  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aAfrika. 4aKultur. 4aMedien. 4aMedientheorie. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aMenschenrechte. 4aPostkolonialismus. 4aRecht. 4aSüdafrika. 4aTransitional Justice. 4aWahrheitskomission. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aAfrica.  aCulture.  aHuman Rights.  aLaw.  aMedia Studies.  aMedia Theory.  aMedia.  aPostcolonialism.  aSouth Africa.  aTransitional Justice.  aTruth Commission.2 aBacklisttransformation EOSC Futureefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2021z9783110753967oZDB-23-DSL08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2021z9783111025100oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839459126?locatt=mode:legacyzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839459126zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839459126/original  a978-3-11-074335-7 DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-DSLb2021  aZDB-23-GOA  aZDB-23-TGPb2021